<p>How open a database protected files (.mdw) using php? Linux/unixODBC/MDBTools/php Working</p>  <pre><code>$query = 'SELECT * FROM MyTable'; $mdb_file = 'example.mdb'; $dataSourceName = "odbc:Driver=MDBTools;DBQ=$mdb_file;"; $connection = new \PDO($dataSourceName); $result = $connection-&gt;query($query)-&gt;fetchAll(\PDO::FETCH_ASSOC); print_r($result); </code></pre>  <p>Does not work</p>  <pre><code>$query = 'SELECT * FROM MyTable'; $mdb_file = 'example.mdb'; $mdw_file = 'wg.mdw';  $dataSourceName = "odbc:Driver=MDBTools;DBQ=$mdb_file;SystemDB=$mdw_file;Uid=admin;Pwd=PASS;"; $connection = new \PDO($dataSourceName); $result = $connection-&gt;query($query)-&gt;fetchAll(\PDO::FETCH_ASSOC); print_r($result); </code></pre>  <p>Thank you.</p>